OL,5,G0330 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,6,     FThere's bad news for George about
OL,7,     Fhis daughter, bad news for Damien
OL,8,     Fabout a bet he's made and bad news
OL,9,     Ffor God about Sally - she's still
OL,10,     Fa Christian...
OL,11,G0400 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,12,     FSally finds God and a somewhat
OL,13,     Fdubious spiritual guide.
OL,14,     FMeanwhile, divorce is on the cards
OL,15,     Ffor George and something even
OL,16,     Fnastier is on the cards for Dave.
